         <div type="edition" xml:lang="kaw-Latn" rendition="class:38769 maturity:83213">
     <p><lb n="1"/>Iki paṅes·tu
        <lb n="2"/>yaṁ mami, guru-gu 
        <lb n="3" break="no"/>ru yen arabi, de<lb n="4" break="no"/>n· kadi botiṁṅ aka<lb n="5" break="no"/>sa lavan· pr̥tivi
        <lb n="6"/>papa kabuk·tih<choice><sic>i</sic><corr>a</corr></choice>,
    </p> 
        <div type="translation" resp="part:argr part:masc">
   <!--translation encoded as per EGD §9.2 -->
        <p>This is the blessing of our god(s). If the teachers mate, let them experience (the consequences of) evil/sin as heavy as heaven and earth combined.</p>
        </div>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
         </div>
